---
// An evolution diagram for the marketing operating model. The point is not the
// final org chart, it is that the system was not designed in one sitting: it
// accreted over about a week, each layer added when a problem made the previous
// shape stop working. Top to bottom is time. The motifs on the right show the
// pieces wiring up from scattered dots into the current hub-and-spoke. Colors
// come from the global theme tokens, so it follows the light/dark toggle.
---

<figure class="ms-figure">
	<svg
		class="ms-evo"
		viewBox="0 0 540 660"
		role="img"
		aria-labelledby="ms-title ms-desc"
		xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
	>
		<title id="ms-title">How the marketing operating model grew</title>
		<desc id="ms-desc">
			A four-stage timeline, top to bottom. Stage one, before May 20: scattered, three
			product builds with no coordination. Stage two, May 22: a single marketing home with a
			freshness checker. Stage three, May 24: the first campaign, with the founder relaying
			product changes. Stage four, May 26: the operating model, a strategy seat, a tactical
			hub, a lead engine, the product, and the founder as the only wire. The motifs on the
			right show disconnected dots progressively wiring into a hub-and-spoke.
		</desc>

		<defs>
			<marker id="ms-arrow2" viewBox="0 0 10 10" refX="8" refY="5" markerWidth="6" markerHeight="6" orient="auto-start-reverse">
				<path class="ms-arrowhead" d="M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z"></path>
			</marker>
		</defs>

		<!-- timeline spine -->
		<line class="ms-spine" x1="40" y1="64" x2="40" y2="604"></line>

		<!-- ===== Stage 1: Scattered (before May 20) ===== -->
		<circle class="ms-dot" cx="40" cy="86" r="6"></circle>
		<text class="ms-eyebrow" x="62" y="62">BEFORE MAY 20</text>
		<text class="ms-stage-title" x="62" y="82">Scattered</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="102">Three product builds, no coordination.</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="116">Marketing was whatever happened</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="130">in the chat that day.</text>
		<!-- motif: loose dots, no edges -->
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="376" cy="72" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="440" cy="62" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="496" cy="90" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="414" cy="112" r="7"></circle>

		<!-- ===== Stage 2: A home (May 22) ===== -->
		<circle class="ms-dot" cx="40" cy="242" r="6"></circle>
		<text class="ms-eyebrow" x="62" y="218">MAY 22</text>
		<text class="ms-stage-title" x="62" y="238">A home</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="258">One marketing home, with a checker</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="272">that flags when the docs drift from the</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="286">real product. Structure, because nothing held.</text>
		<!-- motif: a hub forms, links to the dots -->
		<line class="ms-edge" x1="430" y1="242" x2="374" y2="218"></line>
		<line class="ms-edge" x1="430" y1="242" x2="496" y2="222"></line>
		<line class="ms-edge" x1="430" y1="242" x2="430" y2="284"></line>
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="374" cy="218" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="496" cy="222" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="430" cy="284" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-hub" cx="430" cy="242" r="11"></circle>

		<!-- ===== Stage 3: First campaign (May 24) ===== -->
		<circle class="ms-dot" cx="40" cy="398" r="6"></circle>
		<text class="ms-eyebrow" x="62" y="374">MAY 24</text>
		<text class="ms-stage-title" x="62" y="394">First campaign</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="414">Split what marketing wants from what</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="428">the build ships. I became the relay that</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="442">carries the changes to the product.</text>
		<!-- motif: a relay chain -->
		<line class="ms-edge" x1="369" y1="398" x2="419" y2="398" marker-end="url(#ms-arrow2)"></line>
		<line class="ms-edge" x1="441" y1="398" x2="491" y2="398" marker-end="url(#ms-arrow2)"></line>
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="360" cy="398" r="8"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="430" cy="398" r="8"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node" cx="500" cy="398" r="8"></circle>

		<!-- ===== Stage 4: The operating model (May 26) ===== -->
		<circle class="ms-dot-now" cx="40" cy="554" r="7"></circle>
		<text class="ms-eyebrow ms-eyebrow-now" x="62" y="530">MAY 26 · NOW</text>
		<text class="ms-stage-title" x="62" y="550">The operating model</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="570">A sprint forced the shape it has now:</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="584">a strategy seat, a hub, a lead engine,</text>
		<text class="ms-cap" x="62" y="598">the product, and me as the only wire.</text>
		<!-- motif: the hub-and-spoke -->
		<line class="ms-edge-now" x1="430" y1="554" x2="430" y2="520"></line>
		<line class="ms-edge-now" x1="430" y1="554" x2="374" y2="560"></line>
		<line class="ms-edge-now" x1="430" y1="554" x2="486" y2="560"></line>
		<line class="ms-edge-now" x1="430" y1="554" x2="430" y2="590"></line>
		<circle class="ms-node-now" cx="430" cy="520" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node-now" cx="374" cy="560" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node-now" cx="486" cy="560" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-node-now" cx="430" cy="590" r="7"></circle>
		<circle class="ms-hub-now" cx="430" cy="554" r="11"></circle>
	</svg>
	<figcaption>It was never designed in one sitting. Each layer was added when a problem made the last shape stop working.</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
	.ms-figure {
		margin: 2em 0;
	}
	.ms-evo {
		display: block;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: 480px;
		height: auto;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}
	.ms-evo text {
		font-family: var(--font-stack-sans);
	}
	.ms-spine {
		stroke: var(--rule-strong);
		stroke-width: 2;
	}
	.ms-dot {
		fill: var(--ink);
	}
	.ms-dot-now {
		fill: var(--link-hover);
	}
	.ms-eyebrow {
		fill: var(--ink-faint);
		font-family: var(--font-stack-mono);
		font-size: 10px;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
	}
	.ms-eyebrow-now {
		fill: var(--link-hover);
	}
	.ms-stage-title {
		fill: var(--ink);
		font-size: 16px;
		font-weight: 600;
	}
	.ms-cap {
		fill: var(--ink-muted);
		font-size: 12px;
	}
	.ms-node {
		fill: var(--bg);
		stroke: var(--rule-strong);
		stroke-width: 1.5;
	}
	.ms-hub {
		fill: var(--bg);
		stroke: var(--ink);
		stroke-width: 2;
	}
	.ms-node-now {
		fill: var(--bg);
		stroke: var(--link-hover);
		stroke-width: 1.5;
	}
	.ms-hub-now {
		fill: var(--link-hover);
		stroke: none;
	}
	.ms-edge {
		stroke: var(--ink-muted);
		stroke-width: 1.25;
		fill: none;
	}
	.ms-edge-now {
		stroke: var(--link-hover);
		stroke-width: 1.25;
		fill: none;
		opacity: 0.7;
	}
	.ms-arrowhead {
		fill: var(--ink-muted);
	}
	@media (max-width: 540px) {
		.ms-stage-title { font-size: 15px; }
		.ms-cap { font-size: 11.5px; }
	}
</style>
